title: [1994] Sergey Prokofiev - Complete Piano Sonatas (320kbps)
description:
The complete piano sonatas by Sergey Sergeyevich Prokofiev (1891-1953). These are played by Boris Berman and were recorded in 1994. Ripped from the CD in 320kbps. Enjoy & please seed!
